feedinfo.name: ciscoThreat
feedinfo.tech_data: There are no requirements to share any data to receive this feed.
feedinfo.summary: Cisco Threat Outbreak Alerts address spam and phishing campaigns that attempt to collect sensitive information or spread malicious software by using email attachments or by directing users to malicious sites. These alerts document threats that are active in the wild and provide SenderBase RuleIDs for mitigations; sample email messages; and names, sizes, and MD5 hashes of files.
